text: Five hundred (500) is the natural number after 499 and before 501. In Roman numerals, 500 is written as D. ==Examples== *an HTTP status code for Internal Server Error *in numerology, 500 is believed to be an angel number. Most common versions include 515 and 555. *the years AD 500, 500 BC. == References == Category:Integers
title: 500 (number)
